WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.220
Cheers!

00:30.000 --> 00:33.500
The youth from all over Japan are gathered here.

00:33.500 --> 00:35.500
They are different from each other.

00:35.500 --> 00:38.500
But as friends who love the same God,

00:38.500 --> 00:40.000
they pray together,

00:40.000 --> 00:41.000
pray together,

00:41.000 --> 00:42.000
chat together,

00:42.000 --> 00:43.000
and laugh together.

00:43.000 --> 00:46.500
God will create a new connection.

00:46.500 --> 00:47.500
In the camp,

00:47.500 --> 00:49.500
Japanese, Korean, English,

00:49.500 --> 00:51.500
and three languages are together.

00:51.500 --> 00:54.500
And in the small group discussion,

00:54.500 --> 00:56.000
we have a discussion about

00:56.000 --> 00:58.000
how to become friends

00:58.000 --> 01:00.000
with friends.

01:00.000 --> 01:02.000
There are a lot of games,

01:02.000 --> 01:03.000
activities,

01:03.000 --> 01:04.000
and campfires at night.

01:04.000 --> 01:06.000
There are a lot of programs.

01:06.000 --> 01:08.000
And at the top,

01:08.000 --> 01:10.000
we have the best location

01:10.000 --> 01:11.000
for Mr. Fuji.

01:11.000 --> 01:13.000
In a natural residential school,

01:13.000 --> 01:15.000
we have a little distance from our normal lives,

01:15.000 --> 01:17.000
and we have a 200-day meeting

01:17.000 --> 01:20.000
with friends who have no problems.

01:20.000 --> 01:22.000
It's not just a fun camp,

01:22.000 --> 01:24.000
but a new way of life

01:24.000 --> 01:26.000
with a new dream

01:26.000 --> 01:30.000
will begin.

01:30.000 --> 01:32.000
From August 4th, 2026,

01:32.000 --> 01:33.000
until the 6th,

01:33.000 --> 01:34.000
this summer,

01:34.000 --> 01:35.000
we will experience

01:35.000 --> 01:36.000
something new

01:36.000 --> 01:38.000
that God will begin.

01:38.000 --> 01:41.000
We are looking forward to your participation.

